@startuml
title FitLogger architecture overview

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "FitLogger" {
  [FitLogger] as App
  [Parser] as Parser
  [Command] as Command
  [WorkoutList] as WorkoutList
  [Workout] as Workout
  [ExerciseDictionary] as ExerciseDictionary
  [Ui] as Ui
  [Storage] as Storage
  [UserProfile] as UserProfile
}

database "data/fitlogger.txt" as DataFile
folder "logs/" as Logs

App --> Ui : reads user input
App --> Storage : loadData(profile)
App --> Parser : parse(input, workouts, dictionary)
Parser --> Command : creates command
Parser --> ExerciseDictionary : resolves shortcuts
App --> Command : execute(...)
Command --> Ui : shows output
Command --> WorkoutList : reads/updates workouts
WorkoutList --> Workout : contains
Command --> UserProfile : reads/updates profile
Command --> ExerciseDictionary : reads/updates exercises
Command --> Storage : save/load data
Storage --> ExerciseDictionary : loads/saves shortcuts
Storage --> DataFile : persists workouts/profile
Command ..> Logs : writes diagnostic logs

note right of App
  Creates and owns the shared Ui,
  Storage, WorkoutList, UserProfile,
  and ExerciseDictionary instances.
end note

@enduml
